{"tid":1519280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"We Are In The End Game Now","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:15:19.000Z","uid":19817,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe24b7973dd7a7a7ad2e8c5e7dbfa87b21bece20","tid":1519280,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/4671a2844cf2c889ae86a96aac960033/tenor.gif?itemid=13031245\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F4671a2844cf2c889ae86a96aac960033%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D13031245&h=592cfdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/42d2b65cc9e81d8ca1511c3ad54b4fb8/tenor.gif?itemid=14025047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F42d2b65cc9e81d8ca1511c3ad54b4fb8%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D14025047&h=5b76cf90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共不斷令香港成為國際笑話,  毫無底線去恐嚇, 暴力對待市民, 因為佢地已經無計可施<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">831 將會係END GAME入面既重要轉捩點</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>首先我必需要以正視聽, 我地既敵人係中共, 唔係港共呢班傀儡</strong></span><br />\n中共係呢個世上最奸最無恥既獨裁政權, 佢地既爪牙係世上最冷血既香港公安<br />\n中共將所有野卸落港共班子度, 即使我地成功打敗港共班子, 亦會有另一班港共班子上台<br />\n所以我地係必需要同中共攬炒! 因為唔攬炒係唔可以令香港重光, 唔攬炒既話香港會輸一世<br />\n<br />\n好多人仲認為呢個係香港內部既事情, 可以用時間等佢掉淡,好快就會回復正常, 可以過番開心出街玩出去旅行既生活, 什至有d人呢兩個月都過緊自己既快樂生活, 冇理過下一代既事, 我地絕對唔應該怪佢地想安居樂業既心態, 每個人都係個體, 唔應該去綁架人地做D咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但大家一定要知道香港係企係世界既最前線同中共對抗緊</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要清楚輸左會有咩後果</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果認為之後可以照去旅行</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好意思之後打冷戰之後唔會有得出國</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>如果認為之後可以照無限制上網</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好意思你淨係可以睇央視玩抖音</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果認為香港人仲可以得閒笑下大陸人或者講下政府壞話</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好意思到時你連笑都會俾人拉, 你講一句野都會叛國</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果認為有後路可以移民/拎護照既人可以走佬</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好意思你會被任何莫須有原因禁出境</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你同你既子孫會生生世世成為共產黨既奴隸, <br />\n做香港既二等公民, 俾中共踩曱甴咁踩一世</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何攬炒? 出緊急法就係唔想以解放軍名義出兵,  如果緊急法唔掂...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後天佑香港, 希望大家乖乖地做奴隸, 配合呼籲, 唔好出街, 唔好令事態惡化<br />\n香港已經承受唔起, 俾番安穩既生活香港人!  好食好住聽話就有好生活過!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc641caaefd55951ee2855148b6ae9b02a3a9f0","tid":1519280,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=78adf192\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=11ada43e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e6ad49fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d3445b029c689f71ac20eca6bea4b0487dbf8f47","tid":1519280,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=78adf192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=11ada43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e6ad49fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A